Description: DuckBotOS base system — Weston kiosk + shell utilities
 Minimal base package for DuckBotOS. Installs Weston compositor
 in kiosk mode, agent-facing shell utilities, and security tooling.
 .
 Does NOT include any AI/agent packages — those are in the
 mode-specific packages (duckbotos-hermes, duckbotos-openclaw, etc.).
 .
 Installs:
  - Weston compositor (kiosk/windowed modes)
  - xdg-desktop-portal (Wayland portal for screen capture, file dialogs)
  - fish shell (interactive shell for agents)
  - tmux (terminal multiplexer for sub-agent sessions)
  - firejail + AppArmor (security sandboxing)
  - unattended-upgrades (automated security updates)
  - ufw (uncomplicated firewall)
 .
 Port 5900: VNC for remote desktop access (disabled by default)
